    <Title><![CDATA[Step 1: Create a new module]]></Title>
    <Section>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links>
          <link name="link0" internal="true" type="A">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/the-opencms-workplace/modules-app/]]></target>
