          </link>
        </links>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>Open the <a href="%(link0)">Modules app</a> from the Quick launch menu.</p>
<p>Use the wand icon to create a new module.</p>
<p>Type in <code>org.opencms.examples.formatterconfig</code> as the package name.</p>
<p>Type in a module name and a module description of your choice. Leave the rest as is for now.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
